column3: voter_identification_name
State-issued driver's license
Non-driver ID card issued by a state motor vehicles agency
Photo ID card issued by a public high school in the state
Photo ID card issued by a private high school in the state
Student photo ID issued by public college, university, or postgraduate technical or professional school located within the state
Student photo ID issued by private college, university, or postgraduate technical or professional school located within the state
Photo ID issued by any U.S. educational institution
Health insurance card with a photo
U.S. military photo ID issued by a U.S. uniformed service
Staff photo ID issued by a public college, university or postgraduate technical or professional school located within the state
Staff photo ID issued by a private college, university or postgraduate technical or professional school located within the state
Any identification card issued by an employer in the normal course of business and bearing a photo of the voter, but not including a business card
Employee photo ID card issued by the state in which the voter is registered, the U.S. government or a local government entity within the state
A permit or license to learn to drive a vehicle issued by a state motor vehicle agency
FAA-issued pilot's license
Credit card with photo
Debit card with photo
Health club ID with a photo
ID card with a photo provided by a commercial establishment (e.g., Costco)
Public housing ID card
Public assistance ID
U.S. passport
Certificate of citizenship issued by Citizenship and Immigration Services
Certificate of Degree of Indian or Alaskan Native Blood
Indian census card
Photo identification card issued by a federally recognized Indian tribe in the state
Retirement center ID
Retirement center photo ID from a government-run facility
Neighborhood association ID
U.S. military dependent card
Any other official identification card or license issued by a governmental body of the state or unit of the state government
Photo identification card issued by the U.S. federal government or any agency of the U.S. federal government
Photo identification card issued by a U.S. state or any agency of any U.S. state
